//.Introduction to PHP

PHP stands for Hypertext preprocessor.

PHP is object oriented language. It means it follow the rule of Encapsulation, Polymorphism, Abstraction, Inheritancce.
PHP is Platform Independent it means it can run on any Platform.
PHP is Interpreted language.
PHP is server side scripting Language.

Famous website in Php are Facebook, Yahoo, WordPress, canva, Flipkart,  Twitter, spotify.

HTML directly database se connect nhi hota h, to uske liye php ka use karke HTML ko database se connect karate h. 
php ki jagah Java python C++ hmlog use kar sakte h. 

PHP ko controller bolte h.

XAMPP software is used to for php 
(x=Any Platform either window, Linux, etc)
(A=Apache)
(M=MySQL)
(p=PHP)
(p=Perl)

MVC
HTML,CSS, JavaScript ko View bolte h.
PHP ko controller bolte h.
Database ko model bolte h.

 

